    "These extracted features are then used as input for a classifier, such as a Support Vector Machine (SVM), to distinguish between normal and malicious traffic.",
    "Compared to traditional rule-based or signature-based methods, autoencoders have the potential to enhance the accuracy and efficiency of intrusion detection systems (Ieracitano et al. 2020).",
